      "Generated via AI-assisted analysis of Proverbs 31:10-31. Lady Wisdom connection from Camp's 'Wisdom and the Feminine in Proverbs' and Yoder's 'Wisdom as a Woman of Substance.' Hayil analysis from Waltke's NICOT. Acrostic pedagogy from Fox. Critique of domesticated readings informed by Gafney and Trible."
